                    <span>* TOOL'S RECOMMENDED READING LIST ITEM *
<br />Baignet writes an interesting and controversial speculation, but one must believe that Jesus Christ was actually a person and not just a mythical figure to follow this plot.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Crash course on Christianity</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Helpful: </span>
                      <span>0</span>
